boofcv.alg.feature.detect.quadblob
Class QuadBlob

java.lang.Object
  boofcv.alg.feature.detect.quadblob.QuadBlob

public class QuadBlob
extends java.lang.Object

Contains information on blobs extracted from the binary image. Eventually these blobs are declared to be a square and processed further down the line. Additional data structures have been designed for calibration target detection.

Author:
Peter Abeles
